    <h2>Information we collect</h2>
    <p>We collect your information from you when you create profile by registering our site, subscribe to our newsletter, fill
      out a form or respond to a survey. We request the following personally identifiable information (PII) from you: your name,
      address, e-mail address, telephone number, physical address and date of birth if you place order on our website. We also
      collect your demographic information that is not unique to you such as interests, gender and favorites.</p>
    <p>You may, however, can visit our site anonymously.</p>
    <p>If you choose to use our referring/share service to tell a friend about <%= site_name.capitalize %> or refer a job posting to a friend, your
      friend’s email address is the sole information we’ll ask for this purpose. One-time email inviting your friend to visit
      <%= site_name.capitalize %> website or view the job posting will be sent to your friend. This information will only for this purpose not for
      any other purpose than to send your friend a one-time email. You’ll be provided two options to refer your friends to our site.
      When you choose to access your email account from your <%= site_name.capitalize %> account, and send your personal contacts an email, we only
      use the email information you select by checking the box next to each email to service your request to send this one time email
      from your account.</p>
    <p>Without your explicit consent no email information will be stored from your email account. You can also enter a friend’s email
      directly into the “Invite Colleagues” email field. We do not store this information nor is it shared with any third parties for
      their commercial/promotional purposes.</p>

