      our newsletters and promotional emails.</p>
    <p>If you opted to receive job postings, commercial e-mails or other communications from <%= site_name.capitalize %> or third parties at the time you created
      a <%= site_name.capitalize %> account, but subsequently change your mind, you may opt-out by editing your <%= site_name.capitalize %> Account Profile as described above. If
      you previously opted not to receive such communications, you may later opt-in by editing your <%= site_name.capitalize %> Account Profile as well.</p>
    <p>We retain indefinitely all the information we gather about you in an effort to make your repeat use of <%= site_name.capitalize %>, practical, and relevant.
      Of course, you can delete your resume from <%= site_name.capitalize %>'s online database and close your <%= site_name.capitalize %> account at any time. The procedure for this
